trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"></xref> object in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en komponent redigeringsprogrammet for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection"> </xref> objektet i den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object in the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control at design time, under the control of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>objektet i den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll på utformingstidspunktet under kontroll av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: There is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> associated with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Det er en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>knyttet til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> object is used to apply styles to static submenu items that depend on their level (nesting depth) in the menu structure.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>objektet brukes til å bruke stiler på statisk undermenyelementer som er avhengige av nivåene (nesting dybde) i menystrukturen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor is invoked, for example, by selecting the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer.
trans-unit.target: SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor aktiveres, for eksempel ved å klikke ellipsen (**... **) på den **LevelSubMenuStyles** rad i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A> method always returns `false` to indicate that only one object can be selected at a time in the editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>metoden returnerer alltid `false` til å angi at bare ett objekt kan velges om gangen i redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CanSelectMultipleInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A> method creates a new form to display and edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>Metoden oppretter et nytt skjema for å vise og redigere <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateCollectionForm%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A> method creates a new instance of the specified collection item type.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>metoden oppretter en ny forekomst av den angitte samlingen elementtypen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateInstance%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A> method returns an array of types that the editor can create.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>metoden returnerer en matrise av typene redigeringsprogrammet kan opprette.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor.CreateNewItemTypes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> class when you select, for example, the ellipsis button (**…**) on the **LevelSubMenuStyles** row in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer when designing a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control or a control that is derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> class.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>Når du velger, for eksempel-knappen (**... **) på den **LevelSubMenuStyles** rad i den **Egenskaper** rutenett med den visuelle utformeren når du utformer en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll eller en kontroll som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether multiple <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> elements can be selected in the editor at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om flere <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"> </xref> elementer kan velges i redigeringsprogrammet om gangen.

trans-unit.source: The CanSelectMultipleInstances method always returns `false`; thus, only one <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> object can be selected at a time in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> object.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CanSelectMultipleInstances returnerer alltid `false`; derfor bare én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objekt kan velges om gangen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SubMenuStyleCollectionEditor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>
